EPISOD 3

29
00:03:46,726 --> 00:03:48,061
Selamat datang, Duli Yang Teramat Mulia.

30
00:03:49,271 --> 00:03:51,064
Baginda sedang mencari anda.

31
00:03:51,982 --> 00:03:54,401
